                            <comment id="13181051" author="jcoveney" created="Fri, 6 Jan 2012 02:28:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Find patch attached. I&apos;m not a bash master, so there is slight code repetition...someone else can feel free to make it nicer. It&apos;s affecting production so I went with what worked and was easy &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13181057" author="jcoveney" created="Fri, 6 Jan 2012 02:44:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This fixes a regression that was introduced at some point&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13181105" author="jcoveney" created="Fri, 6 Jan 2012 05:06:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Question: is there a test for bin/pig? I can&apos;t seem to find an obvious one. I&apos;d love to test for this since it&apos;s obviously not super commonly used, but has had a couple of regressions...just nto sure if we already have tests for bin/pig that I can lump this in with.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13181518" author="daijy" created="Fri, 6 Jan 2012 18:58:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There is parameter tests in e2e tests. See test/e2e/pig/tests/nightly.conf, search for section &quot;Parameters&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13181668" author="jcoveney" created="Fri, 6 Jan 2012 22:57:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This adds a simple e2e test&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13181772" author="daijy" created="Sat, 7 Jan 2012 01:46:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1. I will commit it shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13181774" author="daijy" created="Sat, 7 Jan 2012 01:49:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch committed to 0.9/0.10/trunk. Thanks Jonathan!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13182804" author="daijy" created="Mon, 9 Jan 2012 21:12:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2458&quot; title=&quot;Can&amp;#39;t have spaces in parameter substitution&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-2458&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-2458&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-2.patch fix e2e test Parameters_5 failure.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13264116" author="aniket486" created="Fri, 27 Apr 2012 23:40:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I tried to run this on pig-0.9 branch and pig-trunk. This isn&apos;t fixed! &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Try--&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;java -cp pig.jar org.apache.pig.Main -x local -f temp.pig -p &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;NAME=Aniket Mokashi&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;temp.pig-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;a = load &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;1.txt&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
b = foreach a generate &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;$NAME&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
dump b;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Am I missing something?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
